<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{reportName}} — Report from {{agencyName}}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f4f4f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .header { background: #1d4ed8; padding: 32px 40px; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; }
    .header p { color: #bfdbfe; margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body p { color: #374151; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #1d4ed8; color: #fff !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 28px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin: 8px 0 24px; }
    .period { background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .footer { padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>{{reportName}}</h1>
      <p>Scheduled report from {{agencyName}}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi,</p>
      <p>Your scheduled report is ready. Here is the performance summary for the period:</p>
      <div class="period">
        <strong>Period:</strong> {{from}} — {{to}}
      </div>
      {{#if hasAttachment}}
        <p>The PDF report is attached to this email.</p>
      {{else}}
        <p>The PDF report is ready to download. Click the button below:</p>
        <a href="{{downloadUrl}}" class="btn">Download Report</a>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;">This download link is valid for 7 days.</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Sent by AgencyPulse on behalf of {{agencyName}}. To unsubscribe from scheduled reports, contact your agency.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
